* {{PRC}}：[[中华人民共和国外交部|外交部]]发言人[[秦刚|秦刚]]表示，中方对南奥塞梯地区紧张局势升级，发生武装冲突表示「严重关切」。中方呼吁有关方面保持克制，立即停火。衷心希望冲突各方通过对话和平解决争端，以维护该地区的和平与稳定<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/zgsy/news/2008/08-09/1341569.shtml |title=中方对南奥塞梯地区紧张局势表关注 吁立即停火 |accessdate=2014-01-08 |archive-date=2014-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108131851/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/zgsy/news/2008/08-09/1341569.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。外交部亦强调，俄罗斯与喬治亞在[[2008年夏季奥林匹克运动会|奥运会]]期间开战，违背了[[奥林匹克休战|奥运精神]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Russian assault rages as Georgia pulls back|url=http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0,25197,24159598-2703,00.html|publisher=The Australian|date=2008-08-11|accessdate=2008-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080813220209/http://www.theaustralian.news.com.au/story/0%2C25197%2C24159598-2703%2C00.html|archive-date=2008-08-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

* {{CUB}}：支持俄罗斯要求喬治亞从南奥塞梯无条件撤军，[[劳尔·卡斯特罗|劳尔·卡斯特罗]]表示「喬治亞捍卫国家主权是谎言。要求侵略者撤出军队是正当的」，并补充说，南奥塞梯在历史上就是俄罗斯的一部分。劳尔同时谴责美国袒护喬治亞<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/oilRpt/idUKN1030086820080811 |title=Cuba backs Cold War ally Russia on Georgia actions |accessdate=2008-08-13 |archive-date=2008-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080828050215/http://uk.reuters.com/article/oilRpt/idUKN1030086820080811 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
 
* {{FRA}}：「法国一直试图敦促双方达成停火」<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.reuters.com/article/europeCrisis/idUSL844042 |title = West urges end to South Ossetia fighting |publisher = Reuters |accessdate = 2008-08-09 |date = 2008-08-08 |archive-date = 2008-08-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080828172817/http://www.reuters.com/article/europeCrisis/idUSL844042 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

